&lt;Algoma Steel Corp Ltd>said there were no specific developments to explain the recentincrease in its share price and there were no announcementsplanned or anticipated.    The company said it made the statement at the request ofthe Toronto Stock Exchange.    Algoma said it continues to achieve cost reductions andthere is a limited improvement in market demand for thecompany's steel products.    Algoma common closed yesterday in Toronto at 18-1/2, up2-3/4, and was trading today at 18-1/4, down 1/4. Reuter&#3;